<sentence>　ギュ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　つぎの瞬間、どちらともなく固く抱きあってた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
