<paragraph>
<sentence>　トージ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　よかった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ここにこれてよかった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　あなたに会えて、わたしは信じていける。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　いちばん大切なことを。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence>　どんな冬のあとにも、必ず春はくる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　<ruby rubyText="ゆき">雪</ruby><ruby rubyText="ど">溶</ruby>けの<ruby rubyText="ころ">頃</ruby>。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　心に白い花がひらいた日。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　胸を流れるせせらぎ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　彼のシャツに<ruby rubyText="ひ">陽</ruby>ざしの<ruby rubyText="にお">匂</ruby>い。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence>　きっと。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
